name: Twelve Data
title: Twelve Data
description: Financial data provided for developers, to enter the world markets. Instant access for real-time and historical data of stocks, forex, crypto, ETFs, indices, and more. Read more in [documentation](https://twelvedata.com/docs) and start [here](https://twelvedata.com/apikey).

endpoints.name: AD
endpoints.description: Chaikin A/D Line(AD) calculates the Advance/Decline of an asset. This indicator belongs to the group of Volume Indicators.

endpoints.name: Quote
endpoints.description: Quote endpoint is an efficient method to retrieve the latest quote of the selected instrument.

endpoints.name: WCLPRICE
endpoints.description: Weighted Close Price(WCLPRICE) is usually used as the base for other indicators for smoothness. Formula: (high + low + close * 2) / 4.
